PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> 
PREFIX awg: <https://edition.anton-webern.ch/webern-onto#> 

 CONSTRUCT 
 WHERE { 
	 ?subject ?predicate ?object . 
 }

PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/>

PREFIX awg: <https://edition.anton-webern.ch/webern-onto#> 

 CONSTRUCT 
 WHERE { 
	 ?complex a awg:EditionComplex; rdfs:label ?label .  
 }

PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/>

 WHERE { 
	 ?sketch a awg:Sketch . 
 }

PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> 
PREFIX awg: <https://edition.anton-webern.ch/webern-onto#> 

 CONSTRUCT 
 WHERE { 
	 ?paratext a awg:Paratext ; dc:isPartOf awg:Op25_1 . 
 }

PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/>

 }

PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

queryList.queryLabel: Finde alle Objekte, die einer konkomitierenden Skizze vorausgehen
queryList.queryString:
PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> 
PREFIX awg: <https://edition.anton-webern.ch/webern-onto#> 

 CONSTRUCT 
 WHERE { 
	 ?resource a ?resource_class ; awg:precedes ?preceding_sketch .
 ?preceding_sketch awg:concomitates ?concomitating_sketch . 
 }

PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> 
PREFIX awg: <https://edition.anton-webern.ch/webern-onto#> 

 SELECT * 
 WHERE { 
	 ?subject ?predicate ?object . 
 }

queryList.queryLabel: Finde alle Ressource-Klassen und zähle deren Vorkommen
queryList.queryString:
PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> 
PREFIX awg: <https://edition.anton-webern.ch/webern-onto#> 

	 SELECT ?resource_class (COUNT (?resource_class) AS ?count) 
 WHERE { 
	 ?resource a ?resource_class . 
 } 
 GROUP BY ?resource_class 
 ORDER BY ?count 
 LIMIT 100
